#. Tag: title
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:39
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "Popis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kpatience; is a compendium of several well known patience card games, "
"ranging from the well known Klondike and Freecell, to lesser known games "
"such as Grandfather's Clock and Mod3. In all there are 12 variations for you "
"to while away time."
msgstr ""

